001package com.telos.loops.contacts;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonIgnoreProperties;
004
005/**
006 * Response from creating, updating, or deleting a contact.
007 *
008 * <p>This response confirms the operation and provides the contact's ID and a status message.
009 *
010 * @param id the unique identifier for the contact (for create/update operations)
011 * @param message a status message describing the result (e.g., "Contact created", "Contact
012 *     updated")
013 */
014@JsonIgnoreProperties(ignoreUnknown = false)
015public record ContactResponse(String id, String message) {}
